'''Brain damage''' is [[wikt:damage|damage]] to the [[brain]] from either [[illness]]es or [[injury|injuries]]. [[brain cell|Brain]] [[cell]]s are damaged, which often affects one's brain in a way that stops the brain from [[thought|thinking]] or [[reaction|reacting]] the same way as it did before the brain was damaged.

